程序包 src.main.java.Login_story1_3

类 User

java.lang.Object
src.main.java.Login_story1_3.User
public class User extends Object
Title : User.java Description: Represents a user in the login system with JavaFX properties. Stores ID, nickname, encrypted password, email, gender, date of birth, membership type (e.g., VIP or Normal), and expiry date. Provides getters, setters, and property accessors for data binding.

  • 构造器详细资料

    • User

      public User(String ID, String nickname, String password, String email, String gender, String dateOfBirth, String membershipType, String expiryDate)
      Constructs a new User with the specified values.
      参数:
      ID - unique identifier for the user
      nickname - display name or nickname
      password - SHA-256 hashed and Base64 encoded password
      email - user's email address
      gender - user's gender
      dateOfBirth - date of birth in ISO format (yyyy-MM-dd)
      membershipType - "VIP" or "Normal" membership status
      expiryDate - membership expiry date in ISO format, or "null"
